Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:12.10,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}看起来正是休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:15.89,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}又搞错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:19.42,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}即便是这样笨拙的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.54,0:02:22.80,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}能跟我做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.04,0:02:26.83,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真是太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:29.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}唦啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.86,0:02:35.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}飞上天空眺望这小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:39.06,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}与跟大家在一起所见的不尽相同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:41.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真是不可思议呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:44.89,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}像辛辣配菜一样的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:49.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}将每一天都变得多彩
